Description:
    Generates api controller for various models.

    After running the generator, peform the following steps:

    Step 1:
        Add the following code in routes.rb
        namespace :api do
          namespace :v1 do
            resources :your_resource
          end
        end

    Step 2:
        Permit the params in the API controller
        params.permit(:your_first_attribute, :your_second_attribute)

Example:
    rails generate dashboard_base_generator Thing

    This will create:
        what/will/it/create
